race.comment: The well-related WEST CORK (3) (half to G1 winner Qafila) has a handy record around this circuit with two wins and four placings from ten spins and will be rock-hard fit for this. Gets the services of Melbourne Cup-winning hoop Dolan in the saddle and can make his presence felt against this line-up. SAVVY BEE (9) hit the frame last time out and looks ready for the step-up in trip now. Top-three aspirations with Wiggins on top. BATTLESPACE (8) has placed in the past couple and draws the inside marble. Cannot be discounted lightly. BRINGME (10) gets in light with the claim and presents some value for the exotics.
